comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-31T22:18:39.074Z",maintainer-agent,"Unblocked + ready: pm-kfd8 (closed this PR) shipped assertRegisteredImporter/assertRegisteredExporter in src/sdk/testing.ts (match on registrations.importers[].importer / registrations.exporters[].exporter). When pm-todos/pm-beads migrate to api.registerImporter/registerExporter, their package specs should assert via these helpers for non-synthetic first-party importer/exporter exemplars. Finding: no first-party package registers an importer/exporter today, so this item is the real importers-capability exemplar."
